			<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Flynn is right.  It is a bug.  And it isn't restricted to wolves, either, there were a couple of times when ALL the animals in a zone turned into humans.  A friend of mine saw it happen one night in Halas, he petitioned a GM and at the time noone knew why that happened.  Anyways, it was talked about on many sites, and if you go to Dr. Twister's website you may find info and screenshots about it.<BR>
<BR>
A side note, about the crafted quest and werewolves: the crafted breastplate has NOTHING to do with werewolves.  It is gotten in Mistmoore, and werewolves only spawn in West Commons and Karanas, and rarely in East Karana and Kithicor Woods.  The item for the crafted breastplate is the Werewolf Tallon (yes, it's spelled like that) and it drops off of the Gypsy Musician in the castle, same guy who drops that instrument everyone wants.  But you will never get this off of a werewolf, they drop CLAWS which are used in the Lupine Guantlet quest that Karg Icebear of Halas gives you.<BR>
<BR>
Thank you, I run into alot of people every day confused about this.
				</font>
